+    """Decoding settings for the AO's verbalizer generation, env-overridable.
+
+    AO_EVAL_TEMPERATURE lets ao_cli sweep decoding strategy without editing code
+    (mirrors AO_EVAL_STEERING_COEFFICIENT). <=0 selects greedy/deterministic
+    decoding (drops temperature/top_p so transformers doesn't warn); otherwise we
+    sample at the given temperature. Unset = the paper's default (0.7)."""
